{"tid":1884563,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"本土新聞 : 保護傘計劃 -- 在台手足書信","createTime":"2020-02-17T16:10:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-18T12:43:05.000Z","uid":10200,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"ef482eadda6cbddd3a6341c3600934238c86eb5e","tid":1884563,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:10:24.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">㩒link</span> 入面仲有好多手足嘅說話<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.localpresshk.com/2020/02/umbrella-feb-2020/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.localpresshk.com%2F2020%2F02%2Fumbrella-feb-2020%2F&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbK0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=fc9aaa60\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.localpresshk.com/2020/02/umbrella-feb-2020/</a><br />\n<br />\n前言<br />\n<br />\n香港由六月反修例風波開始，現在已超過六千名抗爭者被捕，當中不乏濫捕，在這群人士當中，有不少香港人由香港來到台灣這片自由民主的土地。<br />\n<br />\n未成年的孩子們還能選擇在台唸書，但已成年的青年人卻處於困境當中，由於每日無所事事，加上對未來人生的憂慮和被香港局勢的困擾，漸漸產生了情緒病。有見及此，我們起了《保護傘》計劃的概念，希望在台成立公司，讓滯台港人能就業，讓他們有所托，在台開啟新一頁，重燃人生的燈火。<br />\n<br />\n引用自〈保護傘計劃〉（文：黃國桐律師）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n多謝你哋嘅幫忙，令好似我呢啲要離鄉別井嘅兒女感到有人關心、照顧，使我哋不至大過頻撲無助，多謝你哋令要流亡嘅兒女感到溫暖。光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n前線N<br />\n<br />\n運動過咗大半年，好多手足都要離開香港開始新嘅生活，雖然會唔捨得，但係人無事先做到世界冠軍架！多謝各位有心人嘅支持，令到好迷茫嘅手足見到曙光。喺香港嘅手足都要加油！最緊要身體健康！<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。<br />\n3-2-2020<br />\n前線O<br />\n<br />\n各位同路人你哋要加油，條路好難行但有大家撐住行落去，我哋實會贏。我哋屋企香港會變返之前咁好。光復香港，時代革命<br />\n24-1-2020<br />\n前線P<br />\n<br />\n好感謝尚有人願意對我伸出援手<br />\n好感謝尚有人相信我哋<br />\n出面依家抗爭局勢混亂<br />\n人血饅頭有，呃人有，呃命有，當然有真心嘅<br />\n我自問唔識講野但講事實，信唔信交比人地決定，我講就講左。<br />\n我原本真係真係變左condom，人都唔喺香港，<br />\n係（被）拋棄嘅一群人。<br />\n當我以為我嘅付出不被認可，<br />\n我諗住有咩自己捱，繼續靠自己，<br />\n你地幫過我，我一定會記得。<br />\n我雖然又要離鄉別井又要逃亡，<br />\n但如果比我揀多十次，一百次我都係會咁揀，<br />\n我無後悔過。<br />\n能力越大責任越大。<br />\n其實我做得我預左有今日。<br />\n點都好，感激不盡。<br />\n前線Q"},{"pid":"fca9f6f23f10065381a4927a6434d822bde9c37b","tid":1884563,"uid":71194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:12:13.000Z","msg":"可以點寫信俾佢地"},{"pid":"e9632ab0b21cb8032972163618ea9dfd0c968f4b","tid":1884563,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:12:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db52f745cda29e281258c4e785d193d2d6d4bd58","tid":1884563,"uid":10200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fca9f6f23f10065381a4927a6434d822bde9c37b","tid":1884563,"uid":71194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:12:13.000Z","msg":"可以點寫信俾佢地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:13:55.000Z","msg":"我諗佢地係台灣上到lihkg掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79023074fdfb3f1478dcb75319a4a3f7d1d778ad","tid":1884563,"uid":71194,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db52f745cda29e281258c4e785d193d2d6d4bd58","tid":1884563,"uid":10200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fca9f6f23f10065381a4927a6434d822bde9c37b","tid":1884563,"uid":71194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:12:13.000Z","msg":"可以點寫信俾佢地"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:13:55.000Z","msg":"我諗佢地係台灣上到lihkg掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:18:23.000Z","msg":"你又啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我想講嘅係<br />\n我好愛咁多位手足<br />\n喺台灣有咩需要就出聲<br />\n我地一定會盡力幫手<br />\n喺香港都會繼續努力<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span>"},{"pid":"d3ae4a281391c850dbe5438784477bf96d15a8f2","tid":1884563,"uid":104767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:19:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60c284deab11b081367b1ac35f73ed5b6485a99","tid":1884563,"uid":254183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:32:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c7dd3ec0b1c04c2a98496e7a2e0d09f7fc8f8a","tid":1884563,"uid":43493,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:49:26.000Z","msg":"致流亡手足，和你們的暫別也許是一輩子的事。<br />\n但請好好珍重、裝備自己。<br />\n我見到一場悲劇，瘟疫之下官逼民反。<br />\n不作為的人會在沉默中死去。<br />\n奮身反抗的人會壯烈犧牲。<br />\n為了未來，我們會燃起一片重生的烈火。<br />\n唯有離開了的人回來才能令火海中的亡魂、未亡之人看到希望。<br />\n若你離開了，請在外好好看著我們何以化為飛灰，請記住我們曾經奮戰過。<br />\n期待你們歸來，我們會捨身拼命。<br />\n請你在最後之時照顧我們的家人，在太陽升起之前在外見證一切。<br />\n請好好走上我們用殘軀舖來的勝利階梯。<br />\n願遊子平安。"},{"pid":"e198cf62ca0f261f10022d7a9252ac0687ccd693","tid":1884563,"uid":268519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fca9f6f23f10065381a4927a6434d822bde9c37b","tid":1884563,"uid":71194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T16:12:13.000Z","msg":"可以點寫信俾佢地"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T17:00:58.000Z","msg":"我都想知<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b0c8fd272ea5b09321e189656eeaa3066377d7","tid":1884563,"uid":268519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T17:02:29.000Z","msg":"Like個fb page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%82%98-Aegis-107001547536634/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F%25E4%25BF%259D%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E5%2582%2598-Aegis-107001547536634%2F&d=rocWq0H159RMtn9QCTPVbK0IH4hhGWFtD%2BQErH2Rjq0%3D&h=db3e7fbf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%82%98-Aegis-107001547536634/</a>"},{"pid":"cf6e7dee09e140597a95973a861d32a1a569ede1","tid":1884563,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"59b0c8fd272ea5b09321e189656eeaa3066377d7","tid":1884563,"uid":268519,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T17:02:29.000Z","msg":"Like個fb page<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/%E4%BF%9D%E8%AD%B7%E5%82%98-Aegis-107001