,{"pid":"cf80182b671f498a2ebabd45a9307768159d93ed","tid":1884563,"uid":220977,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T18:01:31.000Z","msg":"各位流亡手足：<br />\n我愛你地<br />\n期待他日迎接你哋歸來既時候<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"4cc830d64c3a2a53a5f9dead99790686cd8f423d","tid":1884563,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd0b87b72ffb758d2c67b1d67719fcd55485f531","tid":1884563,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c09b9ff6848d1a860e0c3f2924f8ad2477aca10f","tid":1884563,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T17:38:18.000Z","msg":"以後打算點，喺台灣是咪可以做嘢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T17:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T23:18:53.000Z","msg":"之前有聽聞過除咗讀書嗰啲，其他已經可以做嘢。好似係議員定個牧師fc咗。<br />\n但應該唔想大肆宣揚，始終台灣難俾難民身份佢哋。台灣暗啞底已經幫咗好多。"},{"pid":"34625057b1d42f638234907e539eb6b8560f25e1","tid":1884563,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T23:19:39.000Z","msg":"如果台灣手足有上連登，希望可以講下現況點。"},{"pid":"94606739c1072361d88044e679c732757ef503e6","tid":1884563,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T01:30:38.000Z","msg":"佢哋依家係台灣安全過喺香港好多，蔡英文政府今次疫情反應實在太好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"004938261138050eaa6613f48dc078470494fa56","tid":1884563,"uid":10200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4cc830d64c3a2a53a5f9dead99790686cd8f423d","tid":1884563,"uid":113155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dd0b87b72ffb758d2c67b1d67719fcd55485f531","tid":1884563,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c09b9ff6848d1a860e0c3f2924f8ad2477aca10f","tid":1884563,"uid":98692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T17:38:18.000Z","msg":"以後打算點，喺台灣是咪可以做嘢"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T17:47:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-17T23:18:53.000Z","msg":"之前有聽聞過除咗讀書嗰啲，其他已經可以做嘢。好似係議員定個牧師fc咗。<br />\n但應該唔想大肆宣揚，始終台灣難俾難民身份佢哋。台灣暗啞底已經幫咗好多。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T01:36:41.000Z","msg":"希望手足係果邊抖下 然後繼續增值自己 讀書又好做嘢又好 係台灣繼續兄弟爬山<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6714f1e204ce29e1e612a8516068ba91f3c9705e","tid":1884563,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T01:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83a4aad91e935ec5d2e3c3f872bc3215dd370122","tid":1884563,"uid":10200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6714f1e204ce29e1e612a8516068ba91f3c9705e","tid":1884563,"uid":105976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T01:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:40:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58537bc76ef7540af8733fddc79b4041d8208ec6","tid":1884563,"uid":59297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-18T12:43:05.000Z","msg":"香港獨立<br />\n<br />\n只有獨立，手足先可以返到嚟"}]}